(15, 'Sudoku', 0, '../../image/Sudoku.PNG', ' <b>  Classic Sudoku is a logic-based number puzzle game and the goal is to place 1 to 9 digit numbers in each grid so that each number can appear only once in each row, each column, and each mini-grid. With our Sudoku puzzle app, you can not only enjoy sudoku games anytime and anywhere, but also learn Sudoku techniques from it. </b>', 8, 1, '2021-05-20 08:17:16', '2021-05-20 12:26:20', '1'),
(16, '2048 Game', 0, '../../image/2048 Game.PNG', '    <div><b>This 2048 game is an upgraded version of the popular classic 2048 game. It not only has the original size (4x4), but also supports small (3x3), large (5x5), larger (6x6) and large (8x8) board sizes. It\'s a surreal 2048 puzzle!</b></div><div><b>HOW:</b></div><div><b>Swipe (Up, Down, Left, Right) to move tiles. When two tiles with the same number of touches, they merge into one. After each swipe, a new tile will appear in an empty space on the board. Slide the tiles to merge, 2 + 2 = 4, 4 + 4 = 8, 8 + 8 = 16, 16 + 16 = 32 ... 64 ... 128 .. 256 .. 512 .. 1024 ... , When 2048 tile is generated, you win!</b></div><div><b>When there is no space on the board and no adjacent tiles with the same value, you lose.</b></div> ', 8, 1, '2021-05-20 08:28:19', '2021-05-20 12:00:21', '1'),
(17, 'Brain Up', 0, '../../image/Brain Up.PNG', '  <b> Brain Up entertainment will enhance your ability and make your brain quick to solve logical and complex puzzles.Let Brain Up take you out of the box with puzzles that require logical thinking. Unlimited creativity and imagination. It won\'t be easy to pass all our brain hack puzzles 2020. Do your best, erase your imagination or seek the help of friends and family! Play smart brain games every day and you will see your brain improve a lot! </b>', 8, 1, '2021-05-20 08:08:21', '2021-05-20 12:39:20', '1'),
(18, 'Defense Zone 2', 68, '../../image/Defense Zone 2.PNG', '  <div class=\"W4P4ne \" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 30px 0px; padding: 0px 50px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;\"><div jscontroller=\"IsfMIf\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" class=\"PHBdkd\" data-content-height=\"144\" jsshadow=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div jsname=\"bN97Pc\" class=\"DWPxHb\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; max-height: none;\"><span jsslot=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><div jsname=\"sngebd\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><b>The game settings are balanced to meet the goals of different players. If you want to test your skills and strategy, you can play the difficult level. If you are just playing for fun, then choose easy or medium level.<br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">Greater variety of weaponry and landscape types gives you huge freedom in choosing your battle tactics. Choose the right weapon type and position to make sure your defense is effective. Airstrikes and the possibility of temporarily increasing weapon power can give you the advantage, and guarantee you will never get bored in the battle process.</b></div></span></div></div><div><div class=\"n1EcZc\" jsname=\"zDTjtb\" jsaction=\"JIbuQc:ornU0b\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 28px 0px 0px; display: inline-block; height: 36px; text-align: center; width: 620p