(104, 'ProShot', 115, '../../image/ProShot.PNG', '<b><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\"The screen layouts are excellent. DSLRs could learn a thing or two from the design of ProShot\"</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">-Engadget</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\"if you can name it, chances are ProShot has it\"</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">-Gizmodo</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">--- CAMERA FEATURES ---</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Auto, Program, Manual, and two fully configur