or: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Zero-lag bracket exposure up to ±3, in 1/3 stop increments*</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Auto ISO option, turns Manual mode into Shutter Priority*</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Manual focus assist*</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Live histogram</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Front-facing camera with exposure control</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Zoom with just one finger</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Fully featured Camera Roll integrated into the viewfinder. View EXIF, support for video playback, media sharing, and delete</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Grid overlay</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Level with 2 different modes</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Adjust JPEG quality, Noise Reduction quality, photo location</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Shortcuts for GPS, screen brightness, camera shutter, and more</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">• Most innovative camera UI ever created</span></b> ', 18, 2, '2021-05-20 12:42:44', '2021-05-20 12:42:44', '1'),
(105, 'Foodie', 0, '../../image/Foodie.PNG', '<div><b>Live your style.</b></div><div><b>The Foodie camera app is an indispensable companion for today\'s social media food enthusiasts.</b></div><div><b>Discover a quick and fun way to spice up the perfect meal experience.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>+ Over 30 professional quality dynamic filters</b></div><div><b>Includes Delicious, Positano, Tropical, Picnic, Sweet, Fresh, BBQ, Romantic, Crispy, and Chewy filter sequences.</b></div><div><b>+ Easy and precise smart guide feature for top-down food photography</b></div><div><b>Capture the perfect atmosphere and mood when photographing food from above.</b></div><div><b>+ Spice up your videos with cool dynamic filters</b></div><div><b>Take a live video of your culinary journey.</b></div><div><b>+ Fix tasteless scenes into colorful masterpieces</b></div><div><b>Use diverse filters and detailed edits to give your photos everything from mesmerizing charm to the warm feel of a film camera.</b></div><div><b>+ Timer to capture the perfect moment</b></div><div><b>Perfect for taking the selfie you want.</b></div><div><b>+ Mute option</b></div><div><b>Enable this option when taking selfies or food photos in quiet restaurants.</b></div><div><b>+ Share photos on social networks</b></div><div><b>Easily share to Instagram, LINE, Facebook, KakaoTalk, WeChat, VSCO, Weibo and many more apps!</b></div><div><b>+ Affiliate apps</b></div><div><b>In addition to the Foodie app, try the B612 and Snow for your other camera needs.</b></div> ', 18, 2, '2021-05-20 12:21:46', '2021-05-20 12:21:46', '1'),
(106, 'FaceU', 0, '../../image/FaceU.PNG', '<div><b>FaceU boasts around 300 million users worldwide, and is currently very popular in Japan and South Korea. Faceu has become a selfie APP used by many fashion icons, internet celebrities and famous stars.</b></div><div><b>There are many updates in the new version that bring better shooting effects to both people and scenes! Special effects including rain control, magic control, and various movie style filters have been updated, making it possible for users to take selfies in new ways every day!</b></div> ', 18, 2, '2021-05-20 12:42:47', '2021-05-20 12:42:47', '1'),
(107, 'Simple Draw Pro', 15, '../../image/Simple Draw Pro.PNG', '<b><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Want to draw something creative but you have no paper? This sketchbook drawing app will suit you perfectly. Just pick a color and start drawing, it is as easy as that. You can either save the drawing in a file, print it or share it directly through email or social networks so that your friends can have some fun with it too. This sketchbook gives you flexibility to draw anything you want with a touch of your finger.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">This hugely popular sketchbook drawing app for quick sketches provides many useful functions like Undo/Redo, changing the background color, or using an image as the background. You can optionally make the app prevent the device from falling asleep too. You can also change the brush size, or use an eraser, if you messed something up. It supports inserting colors either by selecting it on a huge palette, or by entering the colors hex code.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The app supports many different formats like PNG, JPG or SVG vectors. With all these formats, you have an ability to use your sketch however you want. This sketchbook drawing app has kept everything easy for you so you can create masterpieces without worrying for complicated navigations and controls.</span></b> ', 19, 2, '2021-05-20 12:42:54', '2021-05-20 12:42:54', '1'),
(108, 'ArtRage', 67, '../../image/ArtRage.PNG', '<b><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Try out realistic painting and drawing in an app filled with tools that work just like the real thing! Smear oil paint on textured canvas, draw with pencils or pastels on realistic paper, or blend watercolours to create delicate gradients. Unlock your creativity with an easy to use art app that’s great for everyone from kids to professionals.</span><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">You also get powerful digital utilities like Layers and Blend Modes, Tracing and Reference Images to act as guides while painting, and Tool Presets for storing all your favorite settings. All this also comes with support for the expressive features of the Samsung S-Pen, and Android sharing systems so you can show off your art to your friends.</span></b> ', 19, 2, '2021-05-20 12:45:55', '2021-05-20 12:45:55', '1'),
(109, 'X Launcher Pro', 23, '../../image/X Launcher Pro.PNG', '<b style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">X Launcher is designed based on the latest IOS13 style theme, make your phone looks like Phone X with No Ads.<br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">It can completely change the appearance and operation of your phone, giving you an unprecedented experience.</b> ', 19, 2, '2021-05-20 12:11:57', '2021-05-20 12:11:57', '1');
