(115, 'MediBang Paint - Make Art', 0, '../../image/MediBang Paint - Make Art.PNG', '<div><b>MediBang Paint is a FREE lightweight comic book and digital painting program that has a wide range of brushes, built-in fonts, backgrounds, and other resources. MediBang Paint is available for Windows, Mac OS X, Android and iOS. This application uses cloud saving so that users can easily transfer works between platforms.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>The Android version allows users to draw anywhere they want and keep all the features of the desktop version.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>MediBang Paint has a variety of creative tools for illustrators and comic artists. Some of these tools include a variety of brush styles, textures and backgrounds, cloud fonts, and comic creation tools. Finally, when registering for free on the MediBang website, users can access a cloud storage area to easily manage, backup and share their work.</b></div> ', 19, 2, '2021-05-20 13:36:06', '2021-05-20 13:36:06', '1'),
