(120, 'jetAudio HD Music Player Plus', 92, '../../image/jetAudio HD Music Player Plus.PNG', '<div><b>jetAudio Basic is a free music player with Wide, Reverb, Bass Boost sound effects and 10/20 band equalizer.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>jetAudio for Windows is the highest rated and most downloaded multimedia application on CNET.COM, and now you can listen to the same high quality audio on Android with jetAudio.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>It plays almost any music format you have (.wav, .mp3, .ogg, .flac, .m4a, .mpc, .tta, .wv, .ape, .mod, .spx, .opus, .wma*, .mid** and more), it provides very high sound quality with various effects like: Wide, Reverb, X-Bass.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>It comes with 32 preset equalizers that will provide a wider listening experience.</b></div><div><b>For those who want to customize their own audio experience, it also offers 10/20 bands equalizer and other advanced functions including playback speed control, AGC, and more.</b></div><div><b><br></b></div><div><b>The Basic version offers the same features as the Plus version but has ads and lacks some features.</b></div><div><b>To enjoy the full features of jetAdio, purchase the Plus version.</b></div> ', 20, 2, '2021-05-20 13:19:13', '2021-05-20 13:19:13', '1'),
